<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.8.3">
<l>pārā raḷa vumutumunnīr paranta kālam vaḷaimaruppil</l>
<l>ērā ruruvat tēṉamā yeṭutta vāṟṟa lammāṉai</l>
<l>kūrā rāra liraikarutik kuruku pāyak kayaliriyum</l>
<l>kārār puṟavil kaṇṇapurat taṭiyēṉ kaṇṭu koṇṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The powerful lord who, as a boar of beautiful form,</l>
<l rend="indent">lifted [the earth] on his curved tusks,</l>
<l>At the time that the ancient three waters [of the sea]</l>
<l rend="indent">spread until [it] covered the earth,</l>
<l>I, his servant, saw him for myself in Kaṇṇapuram in cloud-covered lands</l>
<l>Where the carp flee when herons spring,</l>
<l rend="indent">intending the pointed āral [fish] as prey.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
